data.description: Check out this 3 bed, 2 bath home sitting on 1.25 acres located in the heart of Alvaton! This home features a covered front and back porch & gracious sized rooms for plenty of space. The MASSIVE owner's suite includes two walk-in closets AND a walk-out screened in private porch. The en suite features a separate stand up shower and whirlpool tub. Outside you will find a detached 2 car garage & plenty of space for a mini farm and garden.  Come lay eyes on this property today!
